    mdecls = set ce.inf_mdecls ∧
    env_rs (se.sem_envM, se.sem_envC, se.sem_envE) se.sem_store (genv,gtagenv,rd) ce.comp_rs bs ∧
    bs.clock = NONE ∧ code_labels_ok bs.code ∧ code_executes_ok' bs`;

